messages.message: Yeah that PR didn’t fix Cypress tests hah. Now I think the cluster is slow which is causing timeout issues =(
oh looks like we’re in a middle of a deployment

:cypress-fire: Would like to get input from others as well and know what has been blocking cypress for people, is it:
1. mainly timeouts
2. or specific test failures?
On my PRs I’ve been mainly seeing timeouts (`ESOCKETTIMEDOUT`, page not loading, etc)
mostly timouts, either the page not loading or uploading a file works but is only ~30% done before the test fails
